{"tid":1096062,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"想聽下連登仔分享下啲超自然經歷","createTime":"2019-04-07T12:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T14:55:51.000Z","uid":164163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad32bc8f7abd422022867eb4abf153de8161ef1","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"即係鬼啊, ufo, 外國怪獸嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟有個朋友曾經喺加拿大嘅軍隊軍訓 曾經試過有一日嘅夜晚要喺戰壕渡過一晚 要8小時內攻佔另一方嘅根據地 所以要摸黑進行 就係當開始咗幾小時後 我朋友同佢啲戰友就聽到有一下好大聲嘅咆哮 沿聲音方向望過去 見唔到任何嘢 但佢哋其中一個就用啲軍人電筒照地下 就見到有好大嘅腳印 仲大過大笨象 不過就得3隻腳趾 2隻喺前面 1隻生喺後面 好似個Y字咁<br />\n<br />\n都係聽我朋友講㗎咋 唔知會唔會係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ba0d3cc784ed2b8203e58a1061be8939206687","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76a637df955318b4ca2687d137d1f6230802f4b6","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d55c1f0006035756ced876ef8ee7f6f51f975bf0","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8db7486c80e32a920cd98d8ba6b0b2d90f7380","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"212b399ed6f946e03bce513f86fc27b9b69659cc","tid":1096062,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e3873ac2fef6c34135a1b1fecf4a7a1e1f3b96b","tid":1096062,"uid":11760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T